    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>《韩流偶像故事: 出道之路》</strong>是一封献给K-pop精彩世界的爱情信笺！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这款人生模拟游戏中，你将化身经纪人，负责发掘人才、安排行程、制定预算、策划社交媒体、挑选音乐并打造偶像形象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的目标？打造下一支风靡全球的K-pop偶像团体！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>挑选你的练习生</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/1df68997e1c9331f12d61bc87124484a.poster.avif?t=1771343089\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/1df68997e1c9331f12d61bc87124484a.webm?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/1df68997e1c9331f12d61bc87124484a.mp4?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每位练习生都拥有独特特质与背景故事：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 某位女孩可能拥有令粉丝疯狂的强烈自信，却也可能破坏团体氛围</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 另一位或许是需要鼓励才能绽放光芒的羞怯歌姬—当她准备登台时，如何应对聚光灯？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为经纪人，你需洞悉她们的故事、性格与优势。组建多元而充满活力的偶像团体，打造完美团队！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>原创K-pop原声带</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/cf6cf4c09f470b496ca432a9dfd47c83.poster.avif?t=1771343089\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/cf6cf4c09f470b496ca432a9dfd47c83.webm?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/cf6cf4c09f470b496ca432a9dfd47c83.mp4?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的偶像团体定位是什么？为她们的首支单曲选择原声带，由K-pop作曲家专为本游戏创作。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>你的选择至关重要</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/c19237e015f59c41eb88607ae5f6bc1f.poster.avif?t=1771343089\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/c19237e015f59c41eb88607ae5f6bc1f.webm?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/c19237e015f59c41eb88607ae5f6bc1f.mp4?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是怎样的经纪人？严谨直率，还是体贴关怀？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•    你会优先取悦唱片公司董事会成员吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >•    你会始终坦诚对待练习生，还是将某些秘密保留到出道当天？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择权在你手中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>解锁并规划日程</strong> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/c4d0ea58b94f4988ed2eb1e692a956f6.poster.avif?t=1771343089\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/c4d0ea58b94f4988ed2eb1e692a956f6.webm?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/c4d0ea58b94f4988ed2eb1e692a956f6.mp4?t=1771343089\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>该让偶像们投入高强度舞蹈训练，还是安排放松身心的瑜伽课程？你的选择将影响团队成长与故事走向。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1662160/extras/04a0d73c9234af47e67b6dfbf549ef48.avif?t=1771343089\" width=800 height=290 /></span></p>",
